      "writtenOn": "2019-01-30T21:23:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Somewhere in docs you should explain what name is used for, including explaining AUTOSCALER_DIMENSION.\n\nAlso mention instances must be the exact set that have AUTOSCALER_DIMENSION\u003dname. (Alternatively, if we want to support subsets, in updateInstanceStatuses, ignore other bots that ListBots might return.)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 116,
        "startChar": 52,
        "endLine": 116,
        "endChar": 63
      },
      "revId": "d54a6eeab0ef78354ecff9b6c53213e8def2becc",
